'''Vallespir''' ({{IPA-ca|ˌvaʎəsˈpi}}) is a [[Comarques of Catalonia|historical Catalan comarca]] of [[Northern Catalonia]], part of the [[France|French]]  [[Departments of France|department]] of [[Pyrénées-Orientales]]. The capital of the comarca is [[Ceret]], and it borders [[Conflent]], [[Roussillon (comarca)|Rosselló]], [[Alt Empordà]], [[Garrotxa]] and [[Ripollès]]. It is in the [[Tech River]] valley. The main towns in the Vallespir are Ceret, Amelie Les Bains, Arles Sur Tech and Prats De Mollo La Preste

